[
  {
    "startTime": 0.5,
    "endTime": 3.19,
    "text": "That's crazy that 25\nyears ago it started."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 3.19,
    "endTime": 4.29,
    "text": "Yeah, it's extraordinary."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 4.29,
    "endTime": 6.57,
    "text": "It's about the most\nrewarding thing"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.57,
    "endTime": 8.31,
    "text": "I could imagine have\nbeing a part of,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 8.31,
    "endTime": 9.9,
    "text": "because it just has\ngone on so long."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.9,
    "endTime": 10.68,
    "text": "But I--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.68,
    "endTime": 11.25,
    "text": "What is this one about?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.25,
    "endTime": 12.45,
    "text": "This is the last one, right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.45,
    "endTime": 16.11,
    "text": "This is about a road trip\nthat Woody ends up on,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.11,
    "endTime": 18.36,
    "text": "and he jumps out and he's\nreunited with Bo Peep."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.36,
    "endTime": 21.88,
    "text": "And also, Key and\nPeele play characters."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.88,
    "endTime": 23.61,
    "text": "And it's loaded."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.61,
    "endTime": 25.08,
    "text": "That there is Tony Hale."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.08,
    "endTime": 27.33,
    "text": "He plays Forky."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.33,
    "endTime": 30.779999999999998,
    "text": "There was there was a major\nthing going on at Pixar,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.78,
    "endTime": 32.22,
    "text": "the originators of that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.22,
    "endTime": 34.86,
    "text": "Is he going to be Forky, or\nis he going to be Sporky,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.86,
    "endTime": 36.3,
    "text": "because in fact--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.3,
    "endTime": 37.699999999999996,
    "text": "he's a spork."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.7,
    "endTime": 41.97,
    "text": "He's a spoon and\na fork all in one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.97,
    "endTime": 44.31,
    "text": "But they felt that that was\ngoing to scare the children,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.31,
    "endTime": 45.36,
    "text": "and so--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.36,
    "endTime": 47.31,
    "text": "they don't want to do\nthat in Pixar movies."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.31,
    "endTime": 49.690000000000005,
    "text": "So they named him Forky."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.69,
    "endTime": 51.089999999999996,
    "text": "The problem with\ndoing the movies"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.09,
    "endTime": 54.25,
    "text": "is you do not get to record\nwith the other people there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.25,
    "endTime": 54.75,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.75,
    "endTime": 55.83,
    "text": "Did you ever do this?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.83,
    "endTime": 57.97,
    "text": "Turn your back to\nthe staff there?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.97,
    "endTime": 61.56,
    "text": "Because there's like, five\nproducers, writers, people"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.56,
    "endTime": 63.6,
    "text": "that are helping you\nout, and they're all"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.6,
    "endTime": 65.82000000000001,
    "text": "sitting at tables looking\nat you, looking at you"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.82,
    "endTime": 66.96,
    "text": "record like this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.96,
    "endTime": 69.145,
    "text": "[LAUGHTER]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.145,
    "endTime": 69.645,
    "text": "Hmm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.645,
    "endTime": 72.78,
    "text": "That was pretty good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.78,
    "endTime": 73.77,
    "text": "What if we try--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.77,
    "endTime": 76.17,
    "text": "and it was making\nme self-conscious."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.17,
    "endTime": 78.3,
    "text": "So for the last\ncouple of sessions,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.3,
    "endTime": 80.66,
    "text": "I turned my back on those punks."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.66,
    "endTime": 82.49,
    "text": "Really?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.49,
    "endTime": 83.55,
    "text": "And did it without them."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.55,
    "endTime": 86.31,
    "text": "Also, because this is\nthe end of the series,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.31,
    "endTime": 89.43,
    "text": "and I had gotten\nsome texts from Tim."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.43,
    "endTime": 92.97500000000001,
    "text": "Tim Allen, who plays Buzz\nLightyear, the astronaut."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.975,
    "endTime": 94.16,
    "text": "[LAUGHTER]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.16,
    "endTime": 98.622,
    "text": "And these texts are saying,\nhave you recorded yet?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.622,
    "endTime": 99.33,
    "text": "Have you been in?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.33,
    "endTime": 100.455,
    "text": "Have you had a session yet?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.455,
    "endTime": 101.42999999999999,
    "text": "I said, no, not yet."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.43,
    "endTime": 102.84700000000001,
    "text": "You haven't seen\nthose last pages?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.847,
    "endTime": 103.94999999999999,
    "text": "No, I haven't seen them."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.95,
    "endTime": 105.325,
    "text": "Wait'll you see\nthose last pages."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.325,
    "endTime": 106.47,
    "text": "Tough one, tough one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.47,
    "endTime": 107.3,
    "text": "Like that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.3,
    "endTime": 107.97,
    "text": "And it was."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.97,
    "endTime": 109.53,
    "text": "The last few sessions where--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.53,
    "endTime": 110.03,
    "text": "Really?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.03,
    "endTime": 113.76,
    "text": "We're saying goodbye\nto Woody and Buzz"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.76,
    "endTime": 116.73,
    "text": "and Bonnie's room and\nAndy and everybody."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.73,
    "endTime": 118.03,
    "text": "It was emotional."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.03,
    "endTime": 118.59,
    "text": "So I had to--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.59,
    "endTime": 119.09,
    "text": "Oh, wow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.09,
    "endTime": 121.59,
    "text": "I had to turn my\nback on them all."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.59,
    "endTime": 123.07000000000001,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.07,
    "endTime": 124.047,
    "text": "I can't wait to see it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.047,
    "endTime": 125.88,
    "text": "I mean, it's going to\nbe sad that it's over."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.88,
    "endTime": 128.03799999999998,
    "text": "Maybe they'll find a way to--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.038,
    "endTime": 128.58,
    "text": "Is it really?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.58,
    "endTime": 129.0,
    "text": "I don't know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.0,
    "endTime": 129.57,
    "text": "Is it over?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.57,
    "endTime": 130.16899999999998,
    "text": "I don't know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.169,
    "endTime": 131.07000000000002,
    "text": "It will live forever."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.07,
    "endTime": 132.32999999999998,
    "text": "That's one thing about it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.33,
    "endTime": 134.38000000000002,
    "text": "You're right, I don't know\nwhy I said-- it's not over."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.38,
    "endTime": 135.17,
    "text": "It'll live forever."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.17,
    "endTime": 135.712,
    "text": "You're right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.712,
    "endTime": 136.7,
    "text": "[LAUGHTER]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.7,
    "endTime": 139.58999999999997,
    "text": "I'm looking forward to a\npossible three-year extension"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.59,
    "endTime": 142.20000000000002,
    "text": "for everybody--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 142.2,
    "endTime": 145.03,
    "text": "All right, we're\ngoing to take a break."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.03,
    "endTime": 146.72,
    "text": "We'll be back."
  }
]